        <updateDate>2022-03-21T22:06:12Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Natural Immunity Transparency Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services to report within 30 days of the bill's enactment to Congress concerning natural immunity to COVID-19.</p> <p>In particular, the report must compare certain outcomes for individuals who recovered from a COVID-19 infection without having received the vaccination and individuals who received the vaccination.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
